 .../crypto/qcom,inline-crypto-engine.yaml     |   1 +
 .../phy/qcom,sc8280xp-qmp-ufs-phy.yaml        |   2 +
 .../devicetree/bindings/ufs/qcom,ufs.yaml     |   2 +
